text.tspan: The Mahasakthi Group is a 300 million US$ Industrial
conglomerate with a strong market presence in several
industrial domains including Textiles, Poultry, Estates,
Renewable Energy, precision Engineering, Trading,
Dealerships, and Premium Property Development. It is
one of the fastest-growing business groups in South
India with a host of group companies and trusts under
its umbrella.
